original_title: ダイナマイト・トラヴァース変奏曲
overview: Dynamite Traverse Variations Tour with members of Chichibu Avantists (Shin Sasakubo × Daisuke Aoki × Haruka Shimizu). In the remains of Koumi stone quarry, original musical scores have been carved into the stone blocks like graphics. Video by Kenji Onishi, directed by Shin Sasakubo.
title: Dynamite Traverse Variations
